Text:
Reason for visit (RFV) current glasses are getting old and wants new ones. Distance and near vision are both good. Just fancies a change. Wears glasses all the time. No contact lenses (CLS).

Symptoms (Sx): No headaches, no eye strain, no redness, no dryness, no double vision (diplopia).

Last eye examination (LEE): Last eye test about 2 years ago.

Ocular history (OH) no problems with eyes in the past, no hospital visits, no infections, hasn't seen doctor (Dr) about eyes, no headaches, no eye strain.

Family ocular history (FOH), nothing relevant, mother reading prescription (Rx).

Family medical history (FMH), no problems.

General health (GH), healthy, no problems, keeps fit, non-smoker.

Medication (meds), none taken, occasional multivitamins in winter.

Occupation, optometry student.

Hobbies, likes reading and playing quidditch.
